title: Kawiarnia Fawory
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan friendly cafe/club offering breakfast sets, snacks and lunch menus, including a vegan burger, tofu scramble, vegan savory pies and sometimes vegan desserts. Healthy and relaxed vibe. Also hosts concerts, exhibitions, workshops. Free Wi-Fi. Outdoor seating during summer.
